caption: A sassy pop-R&B track with snappy finger snaps, groovy bass, and confident female vocals with attitude. Features call-and-response backing vocals, brass stabs, and a strutting beat perfect for empowerment anthems.
lyrics:
[Intro]

Mm hmm

[Verse 1]
Walking in like I own the place
Confidence written on my face
They can talk but I don't care
Flip my hair without a prayer

[Pre-Chorus]
Used to let them dim my shine
But those days are left behind

[Chorus]
I'm that girl yeah you know it's true
Doing things you wish you could do
Can't be stopped won't be denied
Watch me walk with all this pride
I'm that girl

[Verse 2]
Haters gonna hate that's fine
I'm too busy on my grind
Building empires in my name
Playing my own kind of game

[Chorus]
I'm that girl yeah you know it's true
Doing things you wish you could do
Can't be stopped won't be denied
Watch me walk with all this pride

[Bridge]
To all my ladies feeling low
Let your inner goddess show

[Outro]
I'm that girl
Yeah I'm that girl
